<l>meynnilai cuṭṭi ṉellā veḻuttun</l>
<l>tammuṟ ṟāmvarūum raḻavalaṅ kaṭaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When pointing out the situation of the consonants,</l>
<l>all [consonant] sounds except <foreign xml:lang="ta">r</foreign> [and] <foreign xml:lang="ta">ḻ</foreign></l>
<l>can be followed by themselves.<note
              place="foot">In other words, no ' gemination ' of <foreign xml:lang="ta">r</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="ta">ḻ</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
